name: memento mori
description: You need to know death and understand it to have the ecstasy of life. In this work I represented death as a skull, and the ecstasy of life with the work of the master BERNINE "The Ecstasy of Santa Teresa". Thus bringing together the two elements to bring the concept of memento mori. Also adding elements of street art to make reference to the pop world. Art made in D3 using blender and illustration using photoshop.
